## Dogfood (2026-07-14)
Session had two concurrent `hark monitor --for-monitor --replay 0` processes.
Orchestrator received duplicate ambient/watch lines (same event twice).

## Expected
Skill requires one unified monitor; start/bootstrap should be idempotent or
detect an already-running feed consumer.

## Actual
Easy to double-arm across session restarts / dual skill boots.

## Ideas
- Singleflight lock / pidfile for monitor consumers
- `hark monitor` warn if another monitor already tails state
- Skill: check before arming second